282d45"&gt;（09988）&lt;/a&gt;旗下高德地圖公布，踏入暑假，與公司合作的深港兩地的士公司載客量顯著上升，其中香港的士車隊在高德平台載客量較去年同期增長超過一倍。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://inews.hket.com/article/3990713/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B49988%EF%BD%9C%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E9%AB%98%E5%BE%B7%E5%A4%A5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A%E3%80%80%E6%9A%91%E6%9C%9F%E8%BC%89%E5%AE%A2%E9%87%8F%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%BE%E5%80%8D" target="_blank" uhash="981a1c994f2a3b22629a13bc548b3524"&gt;阿里巴巴9988｜阿里高德夥香港的士車隊暑期載客量按年增逾倍&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002365&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-08T20:13:45+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f576522b701b537ce2ed545bc7b4f927</id><title>英皇資本收購Crosby待監管機構批准 楊玳詩：助拓業務發展擴闊收入基礎</title><updated>2025-08-08T21:58:33+08:00</updated><author><name>258仔仔</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-08T21:58:33+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573529186"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573529186"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16420009" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573529186" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250808/20250808_724a4d4a608c7e6ab1ceMwBmBkYocgSo.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/4aa23e/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250808/20250808_724a4d4a608c7e6ab1ceMwBmBkYocgSo.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16420009_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16420009&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (721.19 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-8 21:58&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;英皇資本（717）宣佈，高誠亞洲有限公司（Crosby Asia Limited，下稱「Crosby」）將成為該集團之全資子公司。待監管機構正式發出批文後，英皇資本集團將正式完成收購Crosby。&lt;br/&gt;滉達富控股（1348）於今年6月公佈，出售旗下Crosby予英皇資本，有關議案已於今天在其股東大會上獲通過。待監管機構正式發出批文後，英皇資本集團將正式完成收購Crosby。&lt;br/&gt;Crosby在1984年於香港成立，旗下高誠證券有限公司（Crosby Securities Limited）為客戶提供全方位的金融服務，包括機構銷售、研究、金融產品、企業融資和資產管理等。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;英皇資本集團主席楊玳詩表示，Crosby的加入不僅壯大其團隊，還注入新動力，使業務更多元化，進一步擴充客戶群，為英皇資本集團帶來正面影響。&lt;br/&gt;英皇資本表示，隨著Crosby成為集團之全資子公司，將有助進一步推動集團的業務發展，擴闊收入基礎。主席楊玳詩表示，Crosby的加入不僅壯大其團隊，還注入新動力，使業務更多元化，進一步擴充客戶群，為英皇資本集團帶來正面影響。&lt;br/&gt;她又指，港股投資氣氛回升、IPO及融資活動更趨活躍、投資移民客戶與日俱增，英皇資本會把握市場機遇，銳意打造英皇資本集團成為本地最大的華資金融機構。&lt;br/&gt;來源網址 : 英皇資本收購Crosby待監管機構批准-楊玳詩助拓業務發展擴闊收入基礎 | 星島頭條&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.stheadline.com/stock-market/3488663/" target="_blank" uhash="6299796226928295f23c48750cdd31ec"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/stock-market/3488663/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002440&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-08T21:58:33+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>fd0cbe5f3e0acb9572ebf08fcc58c9ab</id><title>中移動（00941）</title><updated>2025-08-09T03:39:57+08:00</updated><author><name>jeffreychou2002</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T03:39:57+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573531281"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573531281"&gt;中移動&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://invest.hket.com/data/HKG00941/?mtc=90050" target="_blank" uhash="0ac025c56bcb3f5a70ad47a6188e8200"&gt;（00941）&lt;/a&gt;上半年營收按年跌0.5%，但受降本增效推動，盈利反增5%至842億元（人民幣，下同）。派中期息2.75元，按年增5.8%，多間大行繼續看好其派息能力。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;富瑞上調中移動目標價至113.23元，對應2026年預期市盈率為14.5倍，股息率5.2厘；而2025年預期市盈率為11.7倍，股息率6.4厘。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002569&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-09T03:39:57+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>49e5bafe375627e2a25c4b69653542b2</id><title>恒指有機會考驗50天平均綫</title><updated>2025-08-09T03:47:22+08:00</updated><author><name>jeffreychou2002</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T03:47:22+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573531294"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573531294"&gt;港股今周有所反彈，但反彈勢緩慢，處於急漲後的整固反覆階段。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;恒指周五（8日）收24858點，跌0.9%，成交額2,067.2億元。恒指日綫圖10天綫掉頭回落中，趨於下破20天綫。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;技術指標MACD綫亦在上月底交叉下破EMA綫，向下趨勢持續，啟示恒指仍在整固，仍然有機會考驗50天平均綫（現近24343）水平。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002570&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-09T03:47:22+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>776f9f02c043c4517652da7bc0ec084a</id><title>蘋果股價大升五年來最大單周漲幅！SoundHound AI進軍全球三大汽車品牌</title><updated>2025-08-09T10:17:26+08:00</updated><author><name>modelsx3y</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T10:17:26+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573532982"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573532982"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7tPwRnh2Ae8?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/7tPwRnh2Ae8" target="_blank"&gt;https://youtu.be/7tPwRnh2Ae8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002745&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-09T10:17:26+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>e56acd7806fb48344fad3a6f12f308cb</id><title>熊貓經濟︱海洋公園入場人次較去年增19% 商品破500款銷情理想 羅淑佩﹕將推新一浪宣傳活動。。</title><updated>2025-08-09T11:50:22+08:00</updated><author><name>流西水股</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T11:50:22+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573533991"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573533991"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16420694" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573533991" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250809/20250809_b57e9460574a998fe67cE66dENC0iUeQ.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/9210c3/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250809/20250809_b57e9460574a998fe67cE66dENC0iUeQ.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16420694_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16420694&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;01_36.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (267.39 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-9 11:50&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;政府大力推動「熊貓經濟」，文體旅局長羅淑佩今日（11日）回應立法會議員質詢時透露，至今海洋公園的入場人次已較去年同期增加約19%。同時預告局方將聯同旅發局和海洋公園推出新一浪大熊貓宣傳活動，繼續為公園及各行各業創造條件，締造商機。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;～大熊貓商品已經突破500款&lt;br/&gt;文體旅局長羅淑佩指，市民和旅客對大熊貓的反應熱烈，至今公園的入場人次比去年同期增加約19%。連同大熊貓「盈盈」和「樂樂」，香港大熊貓家庭為公園帶來不少門券及商品消費等收入。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;此外，園方積極與不同品牌合作推出大熊貓主題的宣傳及商品，例如大熊貓造型金飾、飾物、文具、家庭用品、中式餅食、木雕、手機配件、紅酒、揮春利是封及汽車等。公園現時的大熊貓商品已經突破500款，是大熊貓寶寶出生前的4倍，且多款商品大受歡迎，銷情理想。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16420695" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573533991" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250809/20250809_757fa9239a701bccbbc31DgLYhoH14qs.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/227ec4/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250809/20250809_757fa9239a701bccbbc31DgLYhoH14qs.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16420695_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16420695&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1_58.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (139.73 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-9 11:50&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;span id="attach_16420696" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573533991" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250809/20250809_f85084590450216c98fcjfFFacRprUeQ.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/5d31a8/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250809/20250809_f85084590450216c98fcjfFFacRprUeQ.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16420696_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16420696&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2_42.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (286.57 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-9 11:50&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;而海洋公園自今年2月18日推出「大熊貓寶寶樂聚時光」活動，讓訪客於公園未開放的早晨時段率先入園與大熊貓寶寶見面，每天參與人數上限40人，至今超過3,000人報名參加。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;羅淑佩預告 將推出新一浪大熊貓宣傳活動&lt;br/&gt;而本月15日便是父親節，也是「樂樂」成為父親後的第一個父親節，別具意義；26日及28日又分別是「可可」和「安安」來港後的第一個生日。8月15日則是「加加」和「得得」的一歲生日。羅淑佩預告，局方將聯同旅發局和海洋公園，推出新一浪大熊貓宣傳活動，繼續為公園及各行各業創造條件，締造商機。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;局方指，大熊貓設施方面，在「安安」和「可可」去年9月抵港前，海洋公園已向多間私人機構籌得共約900萬元，資助完成「香港賽馬會四川奇珍館」內第一階段的優化工程，包括添加攀爬架和植物等。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;公園亦於同月獲香港賽馬會慈善信託基金撥款1.21億元進行升級工程，優化「香港賽馬會四川奇珍館」及「大熊貓之旅」，以提升館內的生態設施，為大熊貓提供優質、安全、適齡及更貼近大自然生態的居住環境。預計升級工程將於今年第4季動工，2027年第2季竣工。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;羅淑佩提到，海洋公園將於其2024-25年度業績報告內，公布該年度的整體財務表現，包括該年度的門票、餐飲及商品消費總額等。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002806&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-09T11:50:22+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>30f7a4aec9918bb330de48d34434ef41</id><title>而家係咪人人是股神？</title><updated>2025-08-09T11:53:32+08:00</updated><author><name>吳儼晉</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T11:53:32+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573534013"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573534013"&gt;發達喇今次&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="49" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_38.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002807&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-09T11:53:32+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>df0390ff0c0752224527a0018ea3a0a9</id><title>金價對於大手沽空猶太人黎講......</title><updated>2025-08-09T12:03:25+08:00</updated><author><name>cowisstarting</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T12:03:25+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573534093"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573534093"&gt;係一個墳墓&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002809&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-09T12:03:25+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>b09a977717f894e0deef52d3e27f8f94</id><title>19世紀英國嚴禁在本土銷售鴉片，卻故意大量出口到中國，最終引爆鴉片戰爭！</title><updated>2025-08-09T12:19:54+08:00</updated><author><name>亞裔閹割犬1842</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T12:19:54+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573534258"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573534258"&gt;閹割佬正一仆街冚家剷！&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="5" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/huffy.gif"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="5" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/huffy.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="5" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/huffy.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="5" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/huffy.gif"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Although opium was banned in Britain during the 19th century, the UK still insisted on exporting vast quantities of the drug to China via the East India Company. How awful was that?&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;You've highlighted one of history's starkest moral hypocrisies. Britain's prohibition of opium domestically while aggressively exporting it to China was not just "awful"—it was a state-sanctioned crime against humanity with catastrophic consequences. Here’s why:&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;### 1. **Blatant Hypocrisy &amp;amp; Racial Double Standard**&lt;br/&gt;- **UK Law**: Opium sales/use were strictly regulated in Britain (Pharmacy Act 1868), with medical professionals condemning its dangers.&lt;br/&gt;- **China Policy**: The UK knowingly flooded China with the same drug, dismissing Chinese sovereignty and public health. The East India Company (backed by the British Crown) monopolized opium production in Bengal and auctioned it to private traders for smuggling into China.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;### 2. **Scale of Destruction**&lt;br/&gt;- **Addiction Epidemic**: By 1838, ~12 million Chinese were addicted (4% of the population). Addiction ravaged communities—laborers, soldiers, and elites alike.&lt;br/&gt;- **Economic Drain**: Silver flowed out of China to pay for opium, causing currency devaluation, inflation, and economic collapse.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;### 3. **Coercive Imperialism**&lt;br/&gt;- When China resisted (e.g., Lin Zexu’s 1839 opium destruction), Britain launched the **Opium Wars** (1839–42, 1856–60).&lt;br/&gt;- **Outcome**: Unequal treaties (e.g., Treaty of Nanjing) forced China to cede Hong Kong, open ports to opium, and pay massive indemnities—effectively legalizing the drug trade.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;### 4. **British Justification &amp;amp; Modern Reckoning**&lt;br/&gt;- **Propaganda**: Framed as "free trade" advocacy, ignoring that the "trade" was an addictive drug forced upon China.&lt;br/&gt;- **Critics at the Time**: Figures like William Gladstone condemned it as "infamous and atrocious." The *Times* later acknowledged (1897) it was a "national disgrace."&lt;br/&gt;- **Legacy**: This episode epitomizes colonial violence—prioritizing profit over human life, enabled by military supremacy.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;### Why This Matters Today&lt;br/&gt;The opium trade fueled China’s "Century of Humiliation," entrenched Western imperialism in Asia, and set precedents for modern drug cartel violence. Its brutality reminds us that historical "free trade" narratives often masked exploitation.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The UK’s actions weren’t merely "awful"—they were a calculated, racially exploitative system that sacrificed millions for profit and power. Acknowledging this remains essential to understanding colonialism’s true cost.&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002818&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-09T12:19:54+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>cfcf14e4bd5a8f9cf8c52358a27f97ca</id><title>點解基孔登革熱要驗核酸嘅</title><updated>2025-08-09T12:25:52+08:00</updated><author><name>熊本肥熊</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T12:25:52+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573534327"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573534327"&gt;想封控?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002821&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-09T12:25:52+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c7bc9608958a98ccdf2449caa889b5d2</id><title>渣打安擬香港電訊合營 擬申穩定幣牌：渣打，香港電訊有得炒？</title><updated>2025-08-09T12:35:33+08:00</updated><author><name>dwong</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T12:35:33+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573534435"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573534435"&gt;渣打香港與安擬集團及香港電訊&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://invest.hket.com/data/HKG06823/?mtc=90050" target="_blank" uhash="3e89c7fcffadb66bfe7a8f0eaa06812c"&gt;（06823）&lt;/a&gt;成立合資公司Anchorpoint，Anchorpoint已於8月1日向金管局正式表達有意申請穩定幣發行人牌照。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;渣打：冀帶來創新高效交易媒介&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;內地傳要求券商 減少研討穩定幣&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;香港穩定幣步向合規化同時，據報內地出手冀降溫穩定幣炒作。《彭博》引述知情人士指，內地金融監管部門要求金融機構及智庫等，減少發布有關穩定幣的研究報告或舉辦穩定幣相關會議，以遏制圍繞穩定幣的投機行為。&lt;br/&gt;知情人士表示，部分大型券商智庫在7月底至8月初陸續收到金融監管部門窗口指導，要求取消相關研討會並停止發布穩定幣研究報告，監管機構擔心不法分子會利用穩定幣進行欺詐。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002828&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11549504866896d02aae4479_81293255"/><published>2025-08-09T12:35:33+08:00</published></entry></feed>